headline: Is Accenture (ACN) a Buy as Wall Street Analysts Look Optimistic?
summary: Based on the average brokerage recommendation (ABR), Accenture (ACN) should be added to one's portfolio. Wall Street analysts' overly optimistic recommendations cast doubt on the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric. So, is the stock worth buying?

headline: US Stock Market Today S&P 500 Futures Slip As Housing And Factory Signals Mix
summary: The Morning Bull - US Market Morning Update Friday, Feb, 27 2026 US stock futures are slightly softer this morning, with E mini S&P 500 contracts down about 0.2% and Nasdaq 100 futures off roughly 0.1%, as investors weigh fresh signals on housing, manufacturing and energy. The 30 year US mortgage rate has slipped back below 6% to 5.98%, which makes monthly payments a bit more manageable and could give the spring housing season a lift.
